==English==

===Noun===
'''melange''' (plural: '''melanges''')

#A [[collection]] containing a variety of [[miscellaneous]] things
#A fictional [[spice]]/[[drug]] originating from [[w:Frank Herbert|Frank Herbert]]'s [[science fiction]] series [[w:Dune (novel)|Dune]]. In the books, the spice is used to [[lengthen]] life, flavor food, heighten [[awareness]], probe the memories of one's [[ancestor]]s, and induce [[prescience]].
#A [[Viennese]] [[coffee]] speciality, consisting of half steamed Milk and half Coffee.

